{"type":"message","id":"7b5cf732","parentId":"39a65483","timestamp":"2026-02-15T14:41:15.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Crafting Deployment Guide**\n\nI'm currently focused on the deployment instructions. I'm building out the `DEPLOY.md` file, aiming for clarity and conciseness. The goal is to make deployment as straightforward as possible for anyone using this. I'm prioritizing step-by-step guidance.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771166475847_301","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Deployment Map\n\n## Commands\n\n1.  **Pull the latest code:**\n    ```bash\n    git pull\n    ```\n\n2.  **Build the Docker image:**\n    ```bash\n    docker-compose build\n    ```\n\n3.  **Run the containers in detached mode:**\n    ```bash\n    docker-compose up -d\n    ```\n\n## Hardware Requirements\n\n*   **CPU:** 4 vCPUs\n*   **RAM:** 8GB\n*   **Disk:** SSD (Network Optimized)\n*   **OS:** Ubuntu 22.04 LTS (recommended)\n\n## Post-Deployment Checks\n\n1.  **Check logs:**\n    ```bash\n    docker-compose logs -f\n    ```\n\n2.  **Verify services are running:**\n    ```bash\n    docker ps\n    ```\n","file_path":"DEPLOY.md"},"thoughtSignature":"CiQBjz1rX/Ac+eJVSzRuP49DkPSWU/tOU8NzZqVqZ5AjjafgdS8KYgGPPWtfDmjWuOZPP9irfvPb20pHpVsEzyVEnEAdMe8Cf3pAW74vFlT/yAt9ja90bYPE1y2ivc+YWE3xyZKnFtP5NSiTIHJNDM0a83REhhEZdTi7YpKX8w96qfcyl610AQbm"}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":7334,"output":208,"cacheRead":5344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7542,"cost":{"input":0.014667999999999999,"output":0.002496,"cacheRead":0.0010688000000000002,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0182328}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771166443213}}
